# Ice Dagger

medieval-spell-speach-ice-dagger = P̭ͅu͕̭̬̓̀̌͛gi͇̲͌ͫo̹͎̟ͨͯ̊ ͙͗̐G̝͗ͨla̩̱c̰̐ǐ̋͋͛à̬ͤͥͨl̫̣̖̅̑͑iͨs̱ͧ

